headline: ZScaler, IBD Stock Of The Day, Eyes Breakout After Cybersecurity Firm's 74% Rally
summary: Zscaler is the IBD Stock of the Day for Thursday. Shares of the cybersecurity firm are approaching a cup base buy point amid a strong year. Shares are already above an early entry. Zscaler stock has rallied 74% year to date.

headline: Armis Integration Could Be a Game Changer for Fortinet’s (FTNT) Cyber Resilience Strategy
summary: Armis and Fortinet recently announced an expanded partnership aimed at simplifying security programs and enhancing cyber resilience for global organizations, integrating Armis Centrix with FortiOS for unified visibility, real-time risk context, and automated enforcement.
